Does anyone have a copy of Audrey Tan's 1998 thesis, "Full completeness for models of Linear Logic" from Cambridge:
https://ethos.bl.uk/OrderDetails.do?uin=uk.bl.ethos.624813
I have tried to find this myself, without success. If you track it down, send me a copy! (-: There should at least be a printed copy somewhere in Cambridge...
